column5: Was fishing a local river last night and after only dragging one lm from the depths I decided to take a run at the local catfish hole.  After 15 or so minutes there I dragged this PB onto the shore. It was night time and all I had was my cell phone so the pic quality is not great but here it is
Nice little kittie there, about 6-7 lbs.   Nothing shabby about that at all. WTG
Where's your fancy gloves???   Have you ever eaten one of those Channel Cats?

lol I think I left my nifty gloves on a rented boat .  No Ive never eaten one but I talked to my dad today and he said they are good eatin, guess its all in how you cook them.  All I know is they smell disgusting coming out of the water.
